original_title: DeSantis sends deputy to retrieve illegal alien fugitive Singh | Fox News
article_summary: Florida Governor Ron DeSantis sends his deputy to California to apprehend an illegal immigrant, Harjinder Singh, accused of killing three people in a fatal crash in Florida. Singh had fled to California, a sanctuary state, after the incident. DeSantis emphasizes that Singh will be held accountable for his actions and will be extradited back to Florida.</s>
